						<span class="tag">Embedded Systems</span>
					</div>
					<div class="project-content">
						<h3>RP2350 High-Speed DAQ</h3>
						<p class="tech-label">C++ • PIO Assembly • UDP</p>
						<p class="short-desc">High-speed data acquisition using the Raspberry Pi Pico 2.</p>
					</div>
				</article>

				<article class="project-card" onclick="document.getElementById('modal-eic').showModal()">
					<div class="project-image" style="background-color: #f0fdf4;">
						<span class="tag">R&D</span>
					</div>
					<div class="project-content">
						<h3>Indoor Farming System</h3>
						<p class="tech-label">Arduino • Sensor Integration</p>
						<p class="short-desc">1st Runner Up in EIC 2020. Automated urban agriculture solution from **SST**.</p>
					</div>
				</article>

				<article class="project-card" onclick="document.getElementById('modal-pico').showModal()">
					<div class="project-image" style="background-color: #e0f2fe;">
