					</div>
				</article>
			</div>

			<dialog id="modal-pico" class="project-modal">
				<div class="modal-header">
					<h2>RP2350 High-Speed DAQ</h2>
					<button class="close-btn" onclick="this.closest('dialog').close()">&times;</button>
				</div>
				<div class="modal-body">
					<p><strong>Overview:</strong> Leveraging the dual-core **RP2350** and its **PIO** blocks to achieve nanosecond-precision timing for physics data capture.</p>
					<ul>
						<li>Interfaced with 8-channel 12-bit ADCs.</li>
						<li>Implemented UDP streaming for real-time monitoring.</li>
					</ul>
					<a href="https://github.com" class="btn-project">View GitHub Source</a>
				</div>
			</dialog>

			<dialog id="modal-eic" class="project-modal">
				<div class="modal-header">
					<h2>Indoor Farming System</h2>
					<button class="close-btn" onclick="this.closest('dialog').close()">&times;</button>
				</div>
				<div class="modal-body">
					<p><strong>Achievement:</strong> Awarded **1st Runner Up** at EIC 2020. This project used **human-centered design** to simplify sustainable urban farming.</p>
					<ul>
						<li>Automated nutrient and water dosing.</li>
						<li>Integrated pH, moisture, and light sensors.</li>
					</ul>
				</div>
			</dialog>
		</main>
		<Footer />

		<script>
			// 1. Modal Backdrop Click-to-Close
			const dialogs = document.querySelectorAll('dialog');
			dialogs.forEach(dialog => {
				dialog.addEventListener('click', (e) => {
					if (e.target === dialog) {
						(dialog as HTMLDialogElement).close();
					}
				});
			});

			// 2. Fade-Up Intersection Observer
			const observerOptions = {
				threshold: 0.1,
				rootMargin: '0px 0px -50px 0px'
			};

			const observer = new IntersectionObserver((entries) => {
				entries.forEach((entry) => {
					if (entry.isIntersecting) {
						entry.target.classList.add('reveal');
						observer.unobserve(entry.target);
					}
				});
			}, observerOptions);

			document.querySelectorAll('.project-card').forEach(card => {
				observer.observe(card);
			});
		</script>
	</body>
</html>

<style>
	/* --- 1. GLOBAL RESET & LAYOUT FIX --- */
	*, *::before, *::after {
		box-sizing: border-box; /* Prevents padding from breaking width */
	}

	html, body {
		margin: 0;
		padding: 0;
		overflow-x: hidden; /* Stops "side-to-side" shaking on mobile */
		width: 100%;
	}

	main {
		/* THE FIX: Pushes content down to clear your fixed header */
		margin-top: 80px; 
		max-width: 1100px; /* Limits width so 2 columns don't get too stretched */
		margin-left: auto;
		margin-right: auto;
		padding: 2rem;
		width: 100%;
	}

	/* --- 2. THE GRID (STRICT 2-COLUMN) --- */
	.projects-grid {
		display: grid;
		/* DESKTOP: Exactly two equal columns */
		grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; 
		gap: 2.5rem;
		width: 100%;
	}

	.projects-hero { 
		text-align: center; 
		margin-bottom: 4rem; 
	}
	
	.projects-hero h1 { 
		color: #0056b3; 
		font-size: 2.5rem; 
	}

	/* --- 3. PROJECT CARD STYLES --- */
	.project-card {
		background: white;
		border-radius: 12px;
		overflow: hidden;
		box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
		border-top: 5px solid #0056b3;
		cursor: pointer;
		width: 100%;
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;

		/* Fade-up Logic */
		opacity: 0;
		transform: translateY(40px);
		transition: 
			opacity 0.8s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1), 
			transform 0.8s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1), 
			box-shadow 0.3s ease;
	}

	/* Triggers via Intersection Observer in your JS */
	.project-card.reveal {
		opacity: 1;
		transform: translateY(0);
	}

	.project-card.reveal:hover {
		transform: translateY(-8px);
		box-shadow: 0 15px 35px rgba(0, 86, 179, 0.15);
	}

	.project-image { 
		height: 180px; /* Slightly taller for the wider 2-column layout */
		padding: 1rem; 
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		justify-content: center;
	}

	.tag { 
		background: #0056b3; 
		color: white; 
		padding: 0.3rem 0.8rem; 
		border-radius: 4px; 
		font-size: 0.75rem; 
		font-weight: bold; 
	}

	.project-content { 
		padding: 1.5rem; 
		text-align: justify; 
		line-height: 1.6; 
		flex-grow: 1;
	}

	.tech-label { 
		font-family: monospace; 
		color: #0056b3; 
		font-weight: bold; 
		margin-bottom: 0.5rem; 
		font-size: 0.9rem;
	}

	/* --- 4. MOBILE RESPONSIVENESS (STRICT 1-COLUMN) --- */
	@media (max-width: 850px) {
		main {
			margin-top: 100px; /* Extra clearance for mobile headers */
			padding: 1.5rem 1rem;
		}

		.projects-grid {
			/* MOBILE: Switch to a single vertical stack */
			grid-template-columns: 1fr; 
			gap: 2rem;
		}

		.projects-hero h1 {
			font-size: 1.8rem;
		}

		.project-content {
			text-align: left; /* Justified text looks better left-aligned on small screens */
		}

		dialog {
			width: 95% !important;
		}
	}

	/* --- 5. MODAL / DIALOG STYLES --- */
	dialog {
		border: none;
		border-radius: 16px;
		padding: 0;
		width: 90%;
		max-width: 650px;
		box-shadow: 0 25px 50px rgba(0,0,0,0.25);
		border-top: 8px solid #0056b3;
	}

	dialog::backdrop {
		background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
		backdrop-filter: blur(4px);
	}

	.modal-header { 
		display: flex; 
		justify-content: space-between; 
		align-items: center; 
		padding: 1.5rem 2rem; 
		background: #f8f9fa; 
		border-bottom: 1px solid #eee; 
	}

	.modal-body { 
		padding: 2rem; 
		text-align: justify; 
		line-height: 1.7; 
	}

	.close-btn { 
		background: none; 
		border: none; 
		font-size: 2rem; 
		cursor: pointer; 
		color: #999; 
	}

	.btn-project { 
		display: block; 
		background: #0056b3; 
		color: white; 
		text-align: center; 
		text-decoration: none; 
		padding: 0.8rem; 
		border-radius: 6px; 
		font-weight: bold; 
		margin-top: 1.5rem; 
	}
</style>
